{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddc02d58f-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1715z–1c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1715z–1c"},"text":"§ 1715z–1c.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Regulation of rents in insured projects","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"After ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1987-12-01"},"text":"December 1, 1987","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development shall control rents and charges as they were controlled prior to "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-04-19"},"text":"April 19, 1983","children":[],"tail":", for any multifamily housing project insured under the National Housing Act ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1701"},"text":"12 U.S.C. 1701","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] if—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddc02d590-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1715z–1c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" during the period of ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-04-19"},"text":"April 19, 1983","children":[],"tail":", through "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1987-12-01"},"text":"December 1, 1987","children":[],"tail":", the project owner and the Secretary have not executed, and the project owner has not filed a written request with the Secretary to enter into, an amendment to the regulatory agreement pursuant to regulations published by the Secretary on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-04-19"},"text":"April 19, 1983","children":[],"tail":", or "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-06-04"},"text":"June 4, 1986","children":[],"tail":", electing to deregulate rents or utilize an alternative formula for determining the maximum allowable rents pursuant to regulations published by the Secretary on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-04-19"},"text":"April 19, 1983","children":[],"tail":", or "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-06-04"},"text":"June 4, 1986","children":[],"tail":"; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddc02d591-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1715z–1c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddc02d592-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1715z–1c/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the project was, as of ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1987-12-01"},"text":"December 1, 1987","children":[],"tail":", receiving a housing assistance payment under a contract pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1437f"},"text":"section 1437f of title 42","children":[],"tail":" (other than under the existing housing certificate program of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1437f/b/1"},"text":"section 1437f(b)(1) of title 42","children":[],"tail":"); or"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddc02d593-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1715z–1c/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" not less than 50 percent of the units in the project are occupied by lower income families (as defined in section 1437a(a)(2) ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002168"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002168"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" Probably should be a reference to section 1437a(b)(2)."}],"tail":" of title 42)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddc02d594-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/242/tIV/s425"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–242, title IV, § 425","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-02-05"},"text":"Feb. 5, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/101/1915"},"text":"101 Stat. 1915","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddc02d595-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddc02d596-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddc02d597-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The National Housing Act, as amended, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1934-06-27/ch847"},"text":"act June 27, 1934, ch. 847","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/1246"},"text":"48 Stat. 1246","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this chapter (§ 1701 et seq.). For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1701"},"text":"section 1701 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddc02d598-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Housing and Community Development Act of 1987, and not as part of the National Housing Act which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
